quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  53,45,"E wonnde O tagii nooneeji …óin : gorel e deyel."
  53,46,"Immorde e to…ď…ďere maniiyu si rufaama e rennga."
  53,47,"E wonnde ko Kanko woodani tagitugol …óin …ói…ói …ďaawo …ói maayude."
  53,48,"E wonnde ko Kanko al…óiniri jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďe yi…óani jawdi, O ye…ói …ďe jawle …óe yim…ďe …óa…ď…ďata."
  53,49,"E wonnde ko Kanko woni Jey…óo hoodere Si'iraa, nde yoga e sirkoo…ďe rewata kafida nde e Allah."
  53,50,"E wonnde ko Kanko halkunoo Aadi'en adinoo…ďe, …ďen woni yim…ďe Huudi …ďen, fewndo …ďe ha…ď…ďitinoo e keeferaaku ngun."
  53,51,"O halki kadi Samuuda'en, yim…ďe Saalih …ďen, O heddinaano hay gooto e ma…ď…ďe."
  53,52,"Ko non kadi O hlkirnoo yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen ado Aadi'en e Samuuda'en. Pellet, yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen laatino …ďur…ďe too√Īude e tii…óude bewre diini Aadi'en e Samuuda'en. Tawde Nuuhu wonnduno e ma…ď…ďe duu…ďi ujunere Ňčakkir…óum cappan…óe jowi, himo nodda …ďe e wootin…óingol Allah, kono …ďe salii nootagol mo."
  53,53,"E ca'e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen …ďen O wayliti haa ka kammu, refti O wayliti …ďe ka leydi."
  53,54,"O hippiri …óe kaa∆īe …óen …óe O hippi e ma…ď…ďe …ďaawo O townude …ďe ka kammu, O li…ďde ka leydi."
  53,55,"Ko hon…óum e neemaaji Joomi maa tinndinay…ói e kattal Makko woni wennjata fii mun, ronkaa waajitorde …óum, an oo ne…ó…óanke?"
  53,56,"Awa oo Nulaa…óo immninaa…óo e mon, ko jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe adinoo…ďe."
  53,57,"Darngal hewtungal ngal …ďadike."
  53,58,"Du√Īoowo ngal itta, maa ∆īellitotoo…óo fii maggal, alaa si wanaa Allah."
  53,59,"E ko ndee yewtere Al*ur'aana janngeteende e dow mon, woni ko haaweto…óon wiide ko ka Allah nde iwri?"
  53,60,"Hi…óon jala jalkita nde, on wullataa tuma nanu…óon waaju mayre?"
  53,61,"Hara ko on weldii…ďe, …ďe haajaaka e mayre?"
  53,62,"Koni sujjanee Allah, la…ď…ďinanon Mo dewal."
  54,1,"Darngal ngal hewtii, lewru ndun kadi seekinoke gila fewndo Annabiijo (jom kisiyee on). Seekagol ndu ngol woni maande laa…ďunde."
  54,2,"Si sirkoo…ďe …ďen yi'ii maande e hujja goongin…óo Nulaa…óo on (yo o his), …ďe …óuurnoo ja…ďugol …óum, …ďe wi'a: …óii hujjaaji e …ďannganduyeeji …ói men yi'i, ko mbilewu meerente."
  54,3,"∆Āe fenni goonga ka o addani …ďe kan, …ďe jokki mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe fennugol ngol. Hara le fiyaaku kala - mo∆ī∆īi maa boni - ko wa…óay…óum no haaniri non √Ďalande Darngal."
  54,4,"Gom…óii kumpite mofte …óe Alllah halkirnoo yeddugol too√Īa arii e ma…ď…ďe, yeru ko …ďe ha…óitora yeddugol too√Īa."
  54,5,"Kon ko ari e ma…ď…ďe, ko √Īe√Ī∆īal timmungal, fii no wonira hujja e ma…ď…ďe. Kono jertingol nafataa yim…ďe …ďe gom…óintaa Allah e √Ďalaande sakkitiinde."
  54,6,"Si …ďe salanike ma an Nulaa…óo, selu …ďe …óuurno…óaa …ďe, habbito…óaa √Īalnde noddoowo halfinaa…óo wuttoygol ngol ka allaandu noddoyta e huunde a√Īiniinde, nde tawata tageefo anndaano sugu mayre ko adii."